Switch Anywhere

Settings switcher for Android, runnable from Notifications.

Currently, only 3 functions available:

 - Accelerometer Rotation : whether the accelerometer will be used to change screen orientation.
 - Bluetooth : whether the bluetooth adapter is enabled.
 - Wi-Fi : whether the wi-fi adapter is enabled.


The application icon is delivered from Tango Icon Library (http://tango.freedesktop.org/Tango_Icon_Library).

